<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 14:07:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>周二，两名以色列国防军预备役士兵在加沙地带北部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/two-idf-reservist-soldeirs-killed-on-tuesday-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-175c-d1f2-a79f-977d21af0000</link><description>这两名士兵被任命为军士长。 （res.）撒迦利亚·佩萨赫·哈伯（Zechariah Pesach Haber）和中士。 Yair Katz 少校；以色列国防军报告称，过去一天有 17 名士兵在加沙地带的战斗中受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 13:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/two-idf-reservist-soldeirs-killed-on-tuesday-in-north-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-175c-d1f2-a79f-977d21af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家在耶路撒冷附近发现了一半非常早期的硬币</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-17/ty-article/israeli-archaeologists-find-half-of-very-early-coin-near-jerusalem/0000018d-174a-d7c2-a1cd-37ce9be60000</link><description>这枚 2,550 年前的硬币是在耶路撒冷第一圣殿时代的住宅中发现的，它已被一分为二，表明它已降级为按重量白银支付的前货币状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 13:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-01-17/ty-article/israeli-archaeologists-find-half-of-very-early-coin-near-jerusalem/0000018d-174a-d7c2-a1cd-37ce9be60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队征召并武装了数千名定居者。关于他们的暴力行为的记录正在堆积如山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-drafted-thousands-of-settlers-accounts-of-their-violence-are-piling-up/0000018d-12e7-d260-aded-b7efddbe0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，“区域防御”营已增加五倍，越来越多的报道称，在其中服役的定居者袭击和威胁巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-army-drafted-thousands-of-settlers-accounts-of-their-violence-are-piling-up/0000018d-12e7-d260-aded-b7efddbe0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟提出扩大警察权力以限制嫌疑人行动的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-advances-bill-expanding-police-powers-to-restrict-suspects-movements/0000018d-170f-d1f2-a79f-977f31d60000</link><description>除其他外，该立法将允许软禁最多 15 天，而目前的软禁时间为 5 天。尽管司法部长反对且紧急政府同意禁止非战争相关立法，但该法案仍在继续推进</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-coalition-advances-bill-expanding-police-powers-to-restrict-suspects-movements/0000018d-170f-d1f2-a79f-977f31d60000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称以色列不会检查加沙人质运送的药品；内塔尼亚胡：“军队有责任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/medicine-for-hostages-arrive-in-egypt-top-hamas-official-israel-wont-inspect-shipment/0000018d-170e-d1f2-a79f-977fdd720000</link><description>哈马斯的阿布·马尔祖克还表示，该协议允许“为人质提供一箱毒品，以换取巴勒斯坦人民的 1,000 箱毒品”。以色列不是该协议的积极参与方，但同意卡塔尔可以自行安排药品和人道主义援助进入加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 11:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/medicine-for-hostages-arrive-in-egypt-top-hamas-official-israel-wont-inspect-shipment/0000018d-170e-d1f2-a79f-977fdd720000</guid></item><item><title>国家撤销对 18 岁以色列人的案件，该男子在司法改革抗议期间被警察殴打</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/state-drops-case-against-18-year-old-israeli-pictured-punched-by-police-officer/0000018d-16dd-d695-a3dd-56fda73e0000</link><description>州检方决定撤销此案，但没有对这一决定做出任何解释。去年夏天警察部长本-格维尔赞扬了这名警官的行为后，警方对该警官的内部调查已经完成，现在正在等待检察官的决定</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/state-drops-case-against-18-year-old-israeli-pictured-punched-by-police-officer/0000018d-16dd-d695-a3dd-56fda73e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的政治和军事领导人想要一场永久的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-political-and-military-leaders-want-a-perpetual-war/0000018d-125e-dac4-a9cf-527fb7820000</link><description>该国许多决策者似乎对以色列与哈马斯的战争持续下去且看不到结束的局面感到着迷。这就是为什么它可以使他们受益</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-political-and-military-leaders-want-a-perpetual-war/0000018d-125e-dac4-a9cf-527fb7820000</guid></item><item><title>由于内塔尼亚胡的政治算计，以色列与哈马斯的人质协议退居二线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</link><description>尽管有美国的压力，内塔尼亚胡唯一担心的“后一天”是拜登之后的事。 ■ 战时内阁因人质释放而陷入分裂，对内塔尼亚胡来说，他的联盟是第一位的。如果甘茨和艾森科特退出紧急政府，可能会在以色列街头引发大规模抗议浪潮</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 04:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔飞机为以色列人质运送药品降落在埃及；两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在隔夜空袭中消灭了计划“迫在眉睫的袭击”的约旦河西岸恐怖组织，巴勒斯坦人报告称，以色列国防军在图尔卡尔姆的空袭中有四人死亡。人质抵达埃及，哈马斯称以色列不会检查他们 ■ 周二，两名以色列国防军预备役人员在加沙战斗中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 03:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部继续发放枪支许可证，以色列却在心理健康检查上磨蹭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</link><description>国家安全部尚未对申请携带武器许可证的以色列人实施扩大且更严格的卫生部调查问卷；本-格维尔的部门表示，调查问卷需要“更加精确”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔证实：为以色列人质提供的药品将于周三进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</link><description>多哈斡旋协议的细节仍不明确，但以色列已同意大幅增加进入加沙的药品数量</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长不停地从一个血腥恐怖场景跳到另一个场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</link><description>周二，我们看到了另一令人作呕的景象，就在一天前，教育部长 Yoav Kisch 在一次恐怖袭击现场加入了一群十几岁男孩的喧闹舞蹈，其中一名妇女被谋杀，另外 17 人受伤，其中许多人伤势严重。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:08:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</guid></item><item><title>世界认真解决巴以冲突吗？我们最好希望如此</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</link><description>“我们不会回到 10 月 6 日”是目前驻中东的外国使节的常见说法。但是，这是什么意思？世界对该地区的战后未来有何设想？两国解决方案如何融入其中？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:32:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里基布兹宣布以色列人质伊泰·斯维尔斯基和尤西·沙拉比死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹宣布这一消息之前，哈马斯周日发布了一段视频，视频中显示两人与另一名以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 在一起</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:25:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</guid></item><item><title>对于阿拉伯以色列人来说，即使是战时的爱国主义也不能抵御赤裸裸的种族主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-16/ty-article/.highlight/for-arab-israelis-even-wartime-patriotism-is-not-a-shield-from-unvarnished-racism/0000018d-12e3-dd15-a7af-9eef0a6f0000</link><description>人们会想象，如果在战争期间不支持以色列会损害阿拉伯-以色列妇女的职业生涯，那么，相反，那些支持以色列事业的人将会得到奖励，而不是受到惩罚。但本周有关电视名人露西·阿哈里什的新闻显示出对阿拉伯人的敌意跨越了政治界限</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 19:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-16/ty-article/.highlight/for-arab-israelis-even-wartime-patriotism-is-not-a-shield-from-unvarnished-racism/0000018d-12e3-dd15-a7af-9eef0a6f0000</guid></item><item><title>沙特外长表示，如果巴勒斯坦问题得到解决，利雅得可能会承认以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-16/ty-article/saudi-foreign-minister-says-riyadh-could-recognize-israel-if-palestinian-issued-resolved/0000018d-12f7-dd15-a7af-9eff2d6e0000</link><description>费萨尔亲王在达沃斯世界经济论坛会议上表示，加沙停火是首要任务，和平只能通过“巴勒斯坦国”实现</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 18:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-16/ty-article/saudi-foreign-minister-says-riyadh-could-recognize-israel-if-palestinian-issued-resolved/0000018d-12f7-dd15-a7af-9eff2d6e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列当局为南部撤离人员预订了双重酒店，部分人被告知离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</link><description>政府将斯德洛特撤离人员在酒店的住宿期限延长至2月底，但酒店已经为基布兹马根撤离人员预订了一月底的住宿。一名仅提前两周通知就被告知离开的撤离者表示，“我们不知所措”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</guid></item><item><title>《辛贝特法》备忘录将使以色列安全机构能够监视记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</link><description>该法律授权情报机构在计算机、手机所有者不知情的情况下对其进行秘密搜查。虽然一些职业在备忘录中受到保护，但记者却不受保护。民权组织称备忘录“忽视了政治影响力的危险”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:16:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</guid></item><item><title>艾美奖与会者对以色列-加沙战争双方表示声援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</link><description>“佩戴具有象征意义的黄丝带不仅具有人类的力量，而且还可以上镜” ■ 演员和业界人士佩戴各种别针，包括黄丝带、鸽子，甚至国际法院的鳞片，以表达对以色列与哈马斯战争的看法</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家监管机构发现国防部多年来忽视患有创伤后应激障碍的残疾退伍军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</link><description>国家审计长发现，用于扩大康复部门的预算的很大一部分尚未得到利用，以色列国防军退伍军人不了解自己的权利，并受到官僚主义障碍和缺乏数字访问的困扰</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</guid></item></channel></rss>